    "section_custom_yFLbUX": {
      "type": "section-custom",
      "blocks": {
        "text_xepqgD": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Why Choose Fenceworks?",
            "text": "<p>If you want to buy a swing set, we have a range of high-quality, durable, safe products to meet every need and budget. With a <a href=\"https://theguyon41.com/collections/playground-one\">Playground One wooden set</a>, your children will be swinging, climbing, and whiling away the days for years to come. </p><p>Unlike big box stores and online retailers, you get personal service with Fenceworks. We started by providing fences in the 1960s, and now the second and third generation of our family work in the business. We can visit your property to provide personalized advice, and we’d also love to see you in our Northbrook showroom - just pop by! </p><p>Whether you need a playset, trampoline, fence, or basketball hoop, contact our family today. We can’t wait to help you! </p>",
            "align": "center",
            "width": "2/3"
          }
        },
        "text_yHcAH6": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Backyard playgrounds, swing sets & outdoor playsets in Chicagoland",
            "text": "<p>If you want to build a backyard playground, swing set, or <a href=\"https://theguyon41.com/\">outdoor playset in the Chicagoland area</a> Fenceworks is the premier detailer. Though there are big chain stores that sell play sets. At Fenceworks, you are dealing with professionals that take your family’s safety as our top priority.  From the customer’s first sales process to our staff of trained installers, our goal is that the entire process is seamless.</p>",
            "align": "center",
            "width": "2/3"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "text_xepqgD",
        "text_yHcAH6"
      ],
