    "section_faq_Q8T7UF": {
      "type": "section-faq",
      "blocks": {
        "category_cMQeRG": {
          "type": "category",
          "settings": {
            "title": "FAQs"
          }
        },
        "article_yAiBnk": {
          "type": "article",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What factors should you consider when designing and purchasing a children's swing set and playset in Chicagoland?",
            "text": "<p>There are many considerations when purchasing outdoor play equipment. During the sales process, we work with our customers asking questions and then listening to the responses to ensure that the right children’s outdoor play equipment or playset is purchased. All of our systems, we know, respond to the most crucial questions parents ask. Is the playset safe? Our goal is for you to buy the right system that can grow with your family.</p>"
          }
        },
        "article_KWpedx": {
          "type": "article",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What safety considerations should you keep in mind when buying a swing set or outdoor playset in Chicagoland?",
            "text": "<p>Though you are looking for a play set, SAFETY comes first. Fun is only secondary. As your children swing, slide, jump, and swing some more, will it hold up?<br/>Was your playset designed to help prevent your children from cutting themselves on sharp bolts or getting caught between bars?<br/>Selecting a playset that has been professionally designed and extensively tested may cost more, the peace of mind it offers is priceless.<br/>Each and every playset you buy from Chicagolands premier playset company is manufactured with either non-splintering vinyl, or constructed from 100% Pacific Solid Cedar with Interlocking Multi-Beam Joint Construction. Our playsets come with:</p>"
          }
        },
        "article_hXp3Cp": {
          "type": "article",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What space considerations should you keep in mind when buying a swing set or outdoor playset in Chicagoland?",
            "text": "<p>Our expertly trained sales staff work with you to guide you toward the appropriate Playset for your family. We take into account your outdoor space. We consider the following in order to keep your children safe and to maximize their fun on their playset:</p><ul><li>Is your backyard large or small?</li><li>Does your yard have tree roots protruding from the ground?</li><li>Does your yard have strangely formed Corners?</li><li>Is your yard level for the crucial “Safety Zone”?</li></ul>"
          }
        }
      },
