    "section_testimonials_atg6zd": {
      "type": "section-testimonials",
      "blocks": {
        "text_UYAhPN": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "media": "stars-brand",
            "svg-code": "",
            "image_round": true,
            "text": "<p>I worked with Fenceworks to have a swing set installed in my backyard. Jake was professional and easy to work with. It was easy to set up the installation with his crew and they arrived right on time. They were communicative and helpful. They even cut some branches from a tree so they wouldn’t be in the way of the swings. Overall it was a positive experience and I highly recommend Fenceworks. My kids love their new swing set!<br/></p>",
            "name": "Carly Friedland Goldstein",
            "source": "Google Reviews"
          }
        },
        "text_zFBtLD": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "media": "stars-brand",
            "svg-code": "",
            "image_round": true,
            "text": "<p>Working with Jake and the Fenceworks team has been a wonderful experience! Jake is so attentive and professional, coming multiple times to my home to ensure that our new trampoline was installed in the ideal and safest location of our yard. Our trampoline is incredible, top of the line quality and safety and I know will be enjoyed for many, many years. Our family has used Fenceworks for swingset installations as well as our experience has always been great. Their products, installation and customer service are superb and I would recommend Fenceworks to all of my family and friends!</p>",
            "name": "Samantha Malach",
            "source": "Google Reviews"
          }
        },
        "text_UwzARL": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "media": "stars-brand",
            "svg-code": "",
            "image_round": true,
            "text": "<p>We had a great experience working with Fenceworks to select and install the right swing set for our backyard. Jake helped us pick the right model, get the best deal possible on it, and ensured installation was as smooth as possible<br/></p>",
            "name": "Brian Slivnick",
            "source": "Google Reviews"
          }
        },
        "text_FfUzRX": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "media": "stars-brand",
            "svg-code": "",
            "image_round": true,
            "text": "<p>Fantastic experience working with Jake and team from start to finish. From picking the perfect swingset to a clean and easy installation, Fenceworks made our family’s dream a possibility!<br/></p>",
            "name": "Michael Zappala",
            "source": "Google Reviews"
          }
        },
        "text_Ew9jEV": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "media": "stars-brand",
            "svg-code": "",
            "image_round": true,
            "text": "<p>Amazing experience. My old swing set broke just weeks before my son’s birthday party. I called Jake and within two weeks. I had a new swingset in my backyard. He made the entire process as easy as it could be.<br/></p>",
            "name": "Rockne Brubaker",
            "source": "Google Reviews"
          }
        },
        "text_CxJBMN": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "media": "stars-brand",
            "svg-code": "",
            "image_round": true,
            "text": "<p>Jake at Fenceworks was fantastic to deal with. He worked with me on building the perfect swingset. Jake was responsive and always took the time to answer my questions and make sure the final product was exactly what I wanted. Couldn’t be happier with fenceworks or my fantastic Swing Kingdom swing set. Highly recommend them both<br/></p>",
            "name": "Rachel Feit",
            "source": "Google Reviews"
          }
        }
      },
